=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/utogashi1.showPublicProfile?language=EN>togashi1</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/10/02 9:45:19 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4054.topic>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Neriak 3rd Gate, Unpickable Firepot - Key Quest?</span><hr size=1> I was wandering in Neriak 3rd gate the other day, its my home city and I have never seen this firepot., but then again I have never wandered around just to look at the place.  It is right at the end of a stone bridge which is a dead end, you will see a rock to the left and the firepot to the right, I clicked on it and it said I did not have a key, so I brought my rog and it said it could not be picked.  Does anyone know where does this firepot lead you to and is there a quest to achieve the key to open it?<br><br>Thanks in advance. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ulomack.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Lomack</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/10/02 12:01:04 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4054.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Neriak 3rd Gate, Unpickable Firepot - Key Quest?</span><hr size=1> You can't get a key to this firepot or any other of the &quot;this lock can not be picked&quot; fire pots.  There is basically one in every city (not SoL or SoV).  The way to use the pots is this.<br><br>In Timmorous Deep there is a room under the water at roughly neg 12200 by pos 4200.  I believe there are spires that stick out of the water for you to see.  In that room are also fire pots.  Each fire pot in each city looks specific to that city.  If you click on the coresponding cities's fire pot you will be teleported to that city.<br><br>The firepot room is the reason that people can no longer bind in TD zone, even casters.  Its one way travel, you can't go back to the fire pot room unless you have the GM key.  It was mentioned long ago when this was first found that the fire pots may have been put in place to allow guides/GMs the ability to move around relatively quickly in the world. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/utanisemanasponge.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Tanise Manasponge</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/10/02 12:02:39 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4054.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Neriak 3rd Gate, Unpickable Firepot - Key Quest?</span><hr size=1> Depends on the story or rumour you hear.<br><br>Either they were for players to move around norrath a little easier.<br><br>They were for GMs to move around norrath a little easier (pre them being able to port).<br><br>They are the port to spot from the firepot room in TD.<br><br><br> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/umyriick.showPublicProfile?language=EN>myriick</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/10/02 1:04:27 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4054.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Neriak 3rd Gate, Unpickable Firepot - Key Quest?</span><hr size=1> the fire pot in TD takes you to just over the water in