ass=m><span class=title> Re: Neriak 3rd Gate, Unpickable Firepot - Key Quest?</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> There is basically one in every city (not SoL or SoV).<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END-->I would <!--EZCODE UNDERLINE START--><u><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> love</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></u><!--EZCODE UNDERLINE END--> to get the locations of those ones.  I've explored most of the cities pretty thoroughly (except Cab) and I've only found 2 in any city (QCat, 3rdGate).  My site is dedicated to these firepots, known as Miragul's Highway.  Though there is no clear connection between the Highway and the TD Room, I've provided a very thorough detailing on the TD Room including the *exact* location (screenshots) to which each pot brings you.<br><br>When I'm not yawning through an XP grind, I'm researching the Firepots. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/udazzlertwodirks.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Dazzler Twodirks</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/10/02 5:33:12 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4054.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Neriak 3rd Gate, Unpickable Firepot - Key Quest?</span><hr size=1> There' one on Odus in the old Necromancer hut in Toxx forest. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ulannellavelglarn.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Lannella Velglarn</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/hottopic.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/10/02 8:16:34 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.co